{"tid":1466623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[不割蓆!!!!!!!!!!!] 對家咁奸，我地不能輕言割蓆！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:27:19.000Z","uid":71037,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4625077a61af9b366f2773bcc56e7036b292e8f7","tid":1466623,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"因為我們是命運共同體！<br />\n自己人會犯錯，你可以睇唔過眼，你可以屌、可以勸，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但千萬不能割蓆！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n團結才是力量，我們是一體的，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要拋低任何自己人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我求下你地！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再互割，我地場運動好快就會玩完</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地就會輸！！</span></span></strong><br />\n7/21 呢？！<br />\n8/11 呢？！<br />\n我地為其他自己人討回公道未？！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雙真普選、5 大訴求呢？！！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">我求下大家啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i